# 詞：銀包

1. 我個銀包唔見咗，成日都搵唔到。 (I lost my wallet and can't find it anywhere.)
2. 你個銀包入面有幾多錢呀？ (How much money is in your wallet?)
3. 唔好將個銀包放喺後袋，坐低會壓爛嘅。 (Don't put your wallet in your back pocket, it'll get crushed when you sit down.)
4. 佢成日都帶住個舊銀包，好似好珍貴咁。 (He always carries that old wallet, as if it were very precious.)
5. 我個銀包入面冇幾多現金，只係有張信用卡同張身份證。 (There isn't much cash in my wallet, just a credit card and an ID card.)
6. 如果唔小心將銀包遺失咗，要即刻報警同通知銀行。 (If you accidentally lose your wallet, you need to report it to the police and notify the bank immediately.)
7. 佢個銀包好細，連張紙幣都放唔落去。 (His wallet is so small that it can't even fit a banknote.)
8. 你個銀包係邊度買㗎？款式好靚喎。 (Where did you buy your wallet? The style is very nice.)
9. 我將個銀包放喺櫃檯上面，你幫我睇住佢好唔好？ (I put my wallet on the counter, can you keep an eye on it for me?)
10. 佢個銀包雖然舊，但係成日都擦得乾乾淨淨。 (Although his wallet is old, he always keeps it very clean.) [end of text]


